name: Zucchini Fritter Crisps
author: Linda at Bit of Flavor
summary: Simple zucchini fritters pair nicely with the lightly-salted crunch of Snack Factory® Pretzel Crisps®. Perfect to serve as a snack or appetizer!
ingredients: 1 large zucchini, grated and drained on paper towels
¾ cup chopped leeks (white and light green parts only)
½ cup vegetable oil for frying
20 each Original Snack Factory® Pretzel Crisps®, or more as needed
directions: In medium bowl, combine zucchini, leeks, eggs, panko, and salt and pepper
Heat 1/2 inch oil in large non-stick skillet over medium-high heat
Form small patties from the zucchini mixture using a spoon; add to hot oil in batches
Cook until golden brown, 2 to 3 minutes per side
Remove from pan and drain on paper towels
Arrange Pretzel Crisps® on a serving tray
Top each crisp with a mini zucchini fritter
Add a drop of ranch dressing, if desired
